				Ok just a little tip whatever class you pick lvl from 1 to 4 then head to North Ro.The reason is newbie loot off fire beetles and lvl 1 skeletons is pretty good.Bye the time you go from 4 to 6 you should have enough money for spells and gear.Once you have full gear and lvl 4 spells i would go back to Akanon and solo kobolds camps till lvl 8.Once you hit lvl 8 go to Rivervale and lvl to 10.Now you can group in North Ro at dervs till 15.Now your 15 you can lvl 19 in Oasis where the loot sucks badly even in orc groups or go to Highhold Pass and lvl at Orcs near zone edge till 19.Now 19 to 27 group at Goblin Guard group.Now 27 to 36 in Warrior Room group.Bye time you have lvled from 15 to 36 you will be loaded in platium and rest of time your life is real easy make platium for nice stuff.<BR>

